Package: themeBayer
Type: Package
Title: GGPlot-Enabled Palettes that Align with Bayer Colors
Version: 0.1.1
Authors@R: c(person("Connor", "Lennon", email = "connor.lennon.ext@bayer.com", role = c("aut", "cre")), person("Spencer", "Matthews", email = 'spencer.matthews@bayer.com', role = c('aut', 'ctb')))
Maintainer: Connor Lennon <connor.lennon.ext@bayer.com>
Description: A function that allows Bayer-Specific themes for creating
    easy color-themed plots for internal or external presentations. Allows for
    both 'official' discrete color scales and 'unofficial' continuous ones.
